 class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係邊撚到咁多補貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:36:01.000Z","msg":"除左農業之類我覺得值得補貼外,其他娛樂產業,非必要產業都無資格拎補貼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"人地開波做生意個陣冇限人數<br />\n依家政府自己鐘意限制人數，仲要9唔搭8咁限人數，唔係政府補貼唔通老細硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府逼人換新型柴油貨車、石油氣的都補貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每逢改變遊戲規矩都預左要比著數人，世界就係咁運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇唔透就代表你唔識政治了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9c4d9cd80e008c93ed23fbc343d2e25a2c40b4","tid":2001970,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:45:56.000Z","msg":"其實佢播返復仇者既話都應該多人睇"},{"pid":"4f827c31779122e9b5965a74028908fcaa802067","tid":2001970,"uid":128014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"播以下呢三套，我日日入場又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 十年<br />\n2. 地厚天高<br />\n3. 返校"},{"pid":"dfb68c95f6309a38c82beb4455eb6523fe8bb403","tid":2001970,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc8bca1896bcb052ef501c82f3cd34cef96b5635","tid":2001970,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"69be96edefad2780bd00757ca70b1f54350cd609","tid":2001970,"uid":48458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9931f361a689fd037cb3b017898669277740c1d","tid":2001970,"uid":124439,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:34:59.00